Setup
=====

Requirements
------------

* Python 3.6+

Installation
------------

Install this library directly into an activated virtual environment::

    $ pip install lolaml

or add it to your `Poetry <https://poetry.eustace.io/>`_ project::

    $ poetry add lolaml

